  <!-- ═══ SEO CONTENT SECTION ═══ -->
  <section class="seo-content-section" aria-label="About Aquiplex">
    <h2>What is Aquiplex?</h2>
    <p>
      Aquiplex is an AI Operating System built for the modern age of productivity and automation. Unlike traditional AI chatbots that simply answer questions, Aquiplex — powered by Aqua AI — acts as your personal intelligence layer. It decomposes your goals into actionable steps, selects the best AI tools for each task, and delivers polished, real-world outputs that you can use immediately.
    </p>
    <p>
      Whether you are a student trying to learn faster, a developer automating repetitive tasks, a creator building content systems, or an entrepreneur launching a startup, Aquiplex is designed to eliminate friction and transform the way you work. The platform brings together a curated directory of over 100 AI tools across writing, coding, image generation, video production, and machine learning — all organized and accessible in one place.
    </p>

    <h3>The Benefits of AI Automation with Aquiplex</h3>
    <p>
      Automation is no longer reserved for large enterprises with dedicated engineering teams. Aquiplex democratizes AI-powered automation for everyone. By simply describing what you want to accomplish, you trigger a chain of intelligent decisions — model selection, task sequencing, output generation — without writing a single line of code or spending hours researching which tool to use.
    </p>
    <p>
      The productivity gains are immediate. Tasks that once took hours — drafting proposals, generating project roadmaps, creating content calendars, building app wireframes — can now be completed in minutes. Aquiplex integrates seamlessly into your workflow, adapting to your style and priorities as you use it more, becoming a genuine extension of your thinking rather than just another tool to manage.
    </p>

    <h3>Why Choose Aquiplex for AI Productivity?</h3>
    <p>
      The AI landscape is crowded. Hundreds of specialized tools exist for writing, image generation, coding assistance, and data analysis — but switching between them is time-consuming and mentally exhausting. Aquiplex solves this context-switching problem by acting as a unified execution layer. You describe your goal once, and the system intelligently routes your request through the right combination of AI capabilities.
    </p>
    <p>
      Aquiplex also offers Execution Bundles — curated, structured workflows for common high-value tasks like launching a startup, growing a social media presence, or building a website. These bundles provide instant, expert-level project plans powered by AI. Coupled with the live workspace, file editor, and real-time preview features, Aquiplex is the most complete AI productivity platform available today.
    </p>

    <nav class="seo-nav-links" aria-label="Internal navigation">
      <a href="/about">About Aquiplex</a>
      <a href="/aqua-ai">Aqua AI Chatbot</a>
      <a href="/aqua-project-engine">Project Engine</a>
      <a href="/bundles">Execution Bundles</a>
      <a href="/categories">Browse AI Tools</a>
    </nav>
  </section>

  <%- include("partials/footer") %>

  <!-- JS -->
  <script>
    document.addEventListener("touchstart", function(){}, true);

    // Aqua popup
    function openAquaAI() {
      const popup = document.getElementById("aquaPopup");
      if (popup) popup.classList.remove("hidden");
    }

    function closeAquaAI() {
      const popup = document.getElementById("aquaPopup");
      if (popup) popup.classList.add("hidden");
    }

    // Close popup on Escape key
    document.addEventListener("keydown", function(e) {
      if (e.key === "Escape") closeAquaAI();
    });

    // Auto-popup after delay
    setTimeout(openAquaAI, 4000);

    // Chip → input fill
    function setPrompt(text) {
      const input = document.getElementById("heroPrompt");
      if (input) { input.value = text; input.focus(); }
    }

    // Hero AI handler
    function runHeroAI() {
      const input = document.getElementById("heroPrompt");
      if (!input) return;
      const value = input.value.trim();
      if (!value) { input.focus(); return; }

      const btn = document.querySelector(".command-run");
      if (btn) {
        btn.innerHTML = '<span class="run-label">Thinking</span><span class="run-icon">...</span>';
        btn.style.opacity = "0.7";
        btn.disabled = true;
      }

      try { localStorage.setItem("aqua_goal", value); } catch(e) {}

      setTimeout(() => {
        window.location.href = "/bundles";
      }, 350);
    }

    // Enter key on input
    const heroInput = document.getElementById("heroPrompt");
    if (heroInput) {
      heroInput.addEventListener("keydown", function(e) {
        if (e.key === "Enter") runHeroAI();
      });
    }

    // Cursor glow on hero (desktop only)
    if (window.matchMedia("(pointer: fine)").matches) {
      (function() {
        const hero = document.querySelector(".hero-os");
        if (!hero) return;
        const glow = document.createElement("div");
        glow.setAttribute("aria-hidden", "true");
        glow.style.cssText = "position:absolute;width:350px;height:350px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(56,189,248,0.12),transparent 70%);pointer-events:none;border-radius:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);z-index:0;transition:left 0.1s,top 0.1s;";
        hero.appendChild(glow);
        hero.addEventListener("mousemove", function(e) {
          const r = hero.getBoundingClientRect();
          glow.style.left = (e.clientX - r.left) + "px";
          glow.style.top  = (e.clientY - r.top)  + "px";
        });
      })();
    }
  </script>

</body>
</html>
